# Program Flow vs Operations

Important distinction.

## Operations

What the system CAN do.

Example:

```python
add_expense()
```

---

## Flow

WHEN and WHY operations happen.

Example:

```text
User chooses menu option
→ add_expense() executes
→ data updates
→ menu reappears
```

Flow orchestrates operations.

